@@TJvXPCustomWinXPBar
Summary
  Base class for XP style group boxes with fixed items.
Description
  Use TJvXPCustomWinXPBar as a base class when creating controls that should mimick the look and feel
  of the navigation bar used in Windows XP. TJvXPCustomWinXPBar handles the basic tasks of creating and
  managing the items that are displayed on its client area as well as the expanding and collapsing of
  the control.

  Do not create instances of TJvXPCustomWinXPBar. Instead, use a derived control, like TJvXPBar.

